00342 Quadruple<T1, T2, T3, T4>::wrap(const char* data, size_t size)
00343 {
00344         assert(data != NULL);
00345         assert(size >= sizeof_value);
00346         std::memcpy(&e1_, data, sizeof_T1);
00347         std::memcpy(&e2_, data + offset_T2, sizeof_T2);
